\" onclick=\"gs(112583)\">3 Ne. 10:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112619\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112619)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112619)\">3 Ne. 12:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112647\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112647)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112647)\">3 Ne. 18:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113246\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113246)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113246)\">D&amp;C 17:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113266\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113266)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113266)\">D&amp;C 18:27-28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110192)\">Heb. 6:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113082\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113082)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113082)\">D&amp;C 1:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111903\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111903)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111903)\">Alma 12:10-11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112031\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112031)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112031)\">Alma 24:30<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109678\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109678)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109678)\">2 Cor. 11:14<